


Start

Input the user grievance

Is the grievance related to a specific department?
Yes -> Send the grievance to the concerned department
No -> Send the grievance to the general grievance department

Is the grievance a duplicate?
Yes -> Notify the user that the grievance has already been registered
No -> Register the grievance in the system

Assign a unique ID to the grievance

Assign the grievance to a designated officer or team

The officer/team assesses the grievance and prepares a resolution plan

The resolution plan is sent to the user for review and approval

If approved, the resolution plan is implemented

If not approved, the user can raise an appeal

The appeal is sent to a higher authority for review and resolution

End
